Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Reagan's policies stalled
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wb1p
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 7 Jun 1981
Reagan's election promises fade away as reality of government begins to dawn over new administration. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less